REPLACE CONDITIONAL DISPATCHER WITH COMMAND
Conditional logic is used to dispatch requests and execute actions.

Create a Command for each action. Store the Commands
in a collection and replace the conditional logic with
code to fetch and execute Commands.

https://kakimotonline.com/2009/02/21/refactoring-to-command-pattern/

